        <mxCell id="enfVvwoSh9q-ExTy_63h-2085" parent="1" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;spacing=5;spacingTop=-20;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" value="&lt;h1&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Efect&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;Serverul destinat administrarii infrastructurii cloud de catre specialistii IT ai furnizorului este configurat si fisierele Ansible sau scripturile bash ce vor fi utilizate pentru a aduce modificari resurselor cloud sunt copiate pe jumphost.&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="305.4" width="170" x="1013" y="248" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="enfVvwoSh9q-ExTy_63h-2086" parent="1" style="image;sketch=0;aspect=fixed;html=1;points=[];align=center;fontSize=12;image=img/lib/mscae/VM_Linux.svg;labelPosition=center;verticalLabelPosition=top;verticalAlign=bottom;labelBackgroundColor=none;" value="Jumphost / Ansible node" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="75.61" width="82.18" x="1056.9099999999999" y="172.39" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="enfVvwoSh9q-ExTy_63h-2088" parent="1" style="shape=image;imageAspect=0;aspect=fixed;verticalLabelPosition=bottom;verticalAlign=top;image=data:image/png,;" value="" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="67" width="90.72" x="1052.6399999999999" y="172.39" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="enfVvwoSh9q-ExTy_63h-2089" parent="1" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;spacing=5;spacingTop=-20;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" value="&lt;h1&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#004c99&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Pasul5:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#004c99&quot;&gt;specialistul IT se conecteaza pe jumphost si incepe sa ruleze playbook-urile Ansible de configurare a masinilor virtuale cat si scripturile bash de intarire a securitatii, cu scopul de a aduce intregul mediu cloud la cerintele operationale si de securitate dorite.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#004c99&quot;&gt;In paralel, ruleaza de pe admin host scriptul 4-test-infrastructure.ps1 pentru a audita deploymentul si a observa daca ceva nu a mers bine.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="308" width="168.74" x="1013.63" y="432" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="enfVvwoSh9q-ExTy_63h-2090" parent="1" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;spacing=5;spacingTop=-20;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" value="&lt;h1&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Efect&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;Dupa ce intreaga infrastructura este modificata cu Ansible si adusa la configuratia dorita, specialistul IT ruleaza playbookul de verificare, luand masuri dupa caz (daca modificarile nu au produs efectul dorit sau nu au asigurat idempotenta).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Din acest punct mediul cloud devine exploatabil in productie si incepe faza de imbunatatire continua.&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="260" width="170" x="1190.5" y="148" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
